XMP-dc:Title: NBA Knicks Rockets
XMP-dc:Subject: Sports
XMP-dc:Description: Three male NBA players grapple for a ball during a game of basketball; one is White and two are of African descent. One of the Black players wears a white jersey that says "New York 10" while the other wears a dark-colored jersey that presumably says "Houston 50" (the letters are partially blocked from view).

XMP-dc:Title: Arizona Thunder
XMP-dc:Subject: Sports
XMP-dc:Description: Members of the Arizona Thunder soccer team stand together for a group photo in what looks to be an indoor medium-sized stadium. Aside from the guards/goal blockers (wearing gloves) and the coaches, most of them wear matching blue t-shirts with their assigned numbers on them. There's a big lightning bolt symbol emblazoned on the floor, matching the smaller version on them atheletes' shirts. All 25 male players are of a variety of ethnicities. Some are lined up in the back standing with their hands behind their backs while others crouch in the front with their hands in front of them.

XMP-dc:Title: Unidentified Landscape
XMP-dc:Subject: Nature
XMP-dc:Description: Photograph of a rocky landscape next to railroad tracks, taken during the day. There are metal towers spread about nearby on the side. A small cluster of buildings rest in one of the carved out pathways of the dry dessertous place. Some vegetation grows sparingly across the landscape. Could be located somewhere rocky and sunny (e.g. Texas, California, or Colorado).

XMP-dc:Title: Abe
XMP-dc:Subject: Portrait
XMP-dc:Description: A White, well-dressed homeless man with greying, long hair poses as a model for a photography class. He wears a visibly stained, dark-colored suit and tie (no hat) with a handkerchief in the left breast pocket. Grey whisker-like hairs sprout from his chin and his eyes are lowered (as if in mid-blink) as he looks downward, slightly away from the camera. There's a flat mole under his left eye and the lines/wrinkles on the skin of his face show he's older in age.

XMP-dc:Title: Texas Music Scene A Cultural Heritage
XMP-dc:Subject: Music
XMP-dc:Description: Colored photograph of a Black musician wearing a black cowboy hat and strumming an orange bass guitar. The Texas flag hangs behnd him on a tan stone wall to the left and a drumset sits behind him on the right. He appears to be on a stage indoors performing a concert. There's a White musician sitting and playing at a brown wooden piano to the left, also wearing a black cowboy hat. The Black musician wears a gray suit while the White musician wears a black top and a shiny silver watch (presumably). Pink flowers drape the walls behind them.
